summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements for storm drain facilities in property located at 1526 Alki Avenue Southwest and 1564 Alki Avenue Southwest (a portion of Tract 15 and portions of Tracts 2 and 3, respectively, of King County Fifth Addition to the City of Seattle, Volume 34 of Plats, page 1); and placing jurisdiction for said easements in Seattle Public Utilities.
committee: Water Resources, Solid Waste and Public Health
